Subject: [PATCH] RDMA/bnxt_re: Avoid accessing the device structure after it
 is freed
References: bnc#1012628
Patch-mainline: 4.19.10
Git-commit: a6c66d6a08b88cc10aca9d3f65cfae31e7652a99

[ Upstream commit a6c66d6a08b88cc10aca9d3f65cfae31e7652a99 ]

